'''''Redemption''''', izwi kandi nka '''''Resgate''''' , ni filimi yo muri  [[Mozambike]] ya 2019 iyobowe na Mickey Fonseca . Iyi nkuru yibanda ku buzima bwubugizi bwa nabi kuko umuntu wambere ahitamo guhindura ubuzima bwe no kuba umubyeyi mwiza nyuma yimyaka ine ariko bikarangira agasubira mubuzima bwubugizi bwa nabi. <ref>https://globalvoices.org/2020/06/29/netflix-picks-up-resgate-the-first-mozambican-film-to-appear-on-the-platform/</ref> Yatorewe ibihembo icyenda kandi yegukana bibiri muri byo muri Afurika Movie Academy Awards . <ref>https://citizen.co.za/lifestyle/2336723/what-to-watch-on-tv-this-weekend-qaphelas-life-is-turned-upside-down-in-isibaya/</ref>

== Icegeranyo ==
Umugabo wagarutse avuye muri gereza amenya ko, mbere gato yo gupfa, nyina yafashe umwenda uteje akaga. Nubwo ashaka guhindura ikibabi gishya, ahatirwa kongera gusubira mubuzima bwicyaha kuko akeneye amafaranga cyane. <ref>http://www.filmfesthamburg.de/en/programm/Film/32663/Resgate</ref> <ref>https://www.netflix.com/title/81273165</ref>

